stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle

  Idle --> CreatingRecord: submit
  CreatingRecord --> DraftCleared: originId returned
  DraftCleared --> Pending
  Pending --> Polling

  Polling --> Created: status completed
  Polling --> Created: timeout

  Created --> EnterOriginWorld: clear pending + show created
  EnterOriginWorld --> [*]

  Polling --> UiExited: user leaves wait page
  UiExited --> Polling: pending resumes
